Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to present, 112 Fairbairn Road, Sunshine West, for lease.

Located on the busy corner of Fairbairn and Somerville Roads, this property offers fantastic exposure to passing traffic, along with easy access to the freeway network. The CBD and Footscray are accessed via Sommerville Road. The freeway network can be accessed via two routes: either Boundary Road Sunshine West entry/exit ramp, or the Grieve Parade Altona entry/exit. 

Key features include:
+ Neighbouring Kennards Hire
+ High clearance warehouse
+ Two container height roller shutter doors
+ Three phase power outlets in warehouse
+ Rear loading for forty foot containers 
+ 10 car parks
+ Office over two levels with kitchenette
+ Amenities with shower
+ Phone lines connected
+ Flexible terms

For further information or to arrange an on-site inspection, please contact the CBRE team.

*approximate
